.:: Zebra puzzle ::.
Color: white, azure, lavender, coral, aquamarine
Nationality: mexican, british, indian, colombian, dutch
Cigar: pall-mall, swisher, chaman, dunhill, montecristo
Beverage: soy-cola, lemonade, cola, juice, sprite
Pet: fish, cat, snake, frog, guinea-pig

1. Nationality:mexican == Color:white
2. Nationality:british == Pet:fish
3. Beverage:soy-cola == Color:azure
4. Nationality:indian == Beverage:lemonade
5. Color:azure is to the right of Color:lavender
6. Cigar:pall-mall == Pet:guinea-pig
7. Cigar:swisher == Color:coral
8. Beverage:cola is in the middle
9. Nationality:colombian is on the far left
10. Cigar:chaman is on the left or right of Pet:cat
11. Cigar:swisher is to the left or right of Pet:frog
12. Cigar:dunhill == Beverage:juice
13. Nationality:dutch == Cigar:montecristo
14. Nationality:colombian is to the left or right of Color:aquamarine

